room_title: Escape room "Trapped in a Room with a Zombie" by Great Room Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 715 N Glenville Dr Suite 440 Richardson TX, 75081
room_description: There is one hungry zombie chained to the wall. Every 5 minutes a buzzer sounds & the chain grows a foot from the wall! In 60 minutes the zombie will be able to reach you, so you have to find the ultimate key to freedom or join the walking dead!
